<h2>Order Confirmation</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>

<p>Thank you for shopping with <strong>KickKart</strong>! Your order <strong>#{{orderNumber}}</strong> has been successfully placed on <strong>{{orderDate}}</strong>.</p>

<p>Here are the details of your order:</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Shipping Address:</strong> {{shippingAddress}}</li>
  <li><strong>Billing Address:</strong> {{billingAddress}}</li>
  <li><strong>Total Items:</strong> {{totalItems}}</li>
  <li><strong>Total Cost:</strong> KES {{totalCost}}</li>
  <li><strong>Estimated Delivery:</strong> {{estimatedDelivery}}</li>
</ul>

<h3>Order Items:</h3>
<table style="width:100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Item</th>
      <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Quantity</th>
      <th style="text-align:left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">Price</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {{#each orderItems}}
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">{{name}}</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">{{quantity}}</td>
        <td style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">KES {{price}}</td>
      </tr>
    {{/each}}
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>You can track your order and view more details by logging into your account.</p>

<p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a>.</p>

